Package: metagenomeR
Title: Analysis Tools for Read-Based Shotgun Metagenomic Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Adam", "Sorbie", , "adamsorbie@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive toolkit for analyzing read-based shotgun
    metagenomic data. Includes functions for importing taxonomic and functional
    profiles from MetaPhlAn and HUMAnN, calculating alpha and beta diversity
    metrics, performing differential abundance analysis via MaAsLin2, and
    generating publication-ready visualizations including PCA/PCoA ordination
    plots, boxplots, scatter plots, and volcano plots.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/adamsorbie/metagenomeR
BugReports: https://github.com/adamsorbie/metagenomeR/issues
